{"tid":2201931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「冒認黃國英唔見咁快拉」","createTime":"2020-09-14T07:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T09:37:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b38a0f47b24e7fae2081e8f2f6964a745aa1d358","tid":2201931,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200914/C73J6QOGYVG6RA7QEKOEDRPDNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200914%2FC73J6QOGYVG6RA7QEKOEDRPDNY%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=c4fcedda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200914%2FC73J6QOGYVG6RA7QEKOEDRPDNY%2F&h=c7fed0d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200914/C73J6QOGYVG6RA7QEKOEDRPDNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「冒認黃國英唔見咁快拉」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xkI-BHIYiNuo0Jw-vC3-0-ICCl8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ALT7OHA3XNCCXGJB72WXHW4PME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxkI-BHIYiNuo0Jw-vC3-0-ICCl8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FALT7OHA3XNCCXGJB72WXHW4PME.jpg&h=f80b9929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方日前就壹傳媒股價案開記者會，證監事後發聲明暗寸警方搶查。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早於壹傳媒（282）爆升前，市場出現大量「微信女」及假扮財經名人的金融騙案，惟警方未有以同等速度調查。黃偉康批評政治凌駕一切的歪風，令香港失去以往食四方飯的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃偉康指未獲警方聯絡  證監兩度查問壹傳媒急升<br />\n<br />\n黃偉康指市場有更多事件值得調查，如冒認黃國英與陳永陸等名人，於telegram發假消息的集團，「開假黃國英、陸叔推介群組，引人落叠嗰啲又唔見咁快拉到，我覺得對陸叔、黃國英好唔公平囉」；黃偉康為苦主抱不平，「我同陸叔（陳永陸）傾過電話，都認為監管當局無視問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘆政治掛帥 難食四方飯<br />\n<br />\n黃又舉例去年被舞高弄低的股票，警方皆沒調查執法，如雅高控股（3313）沒成交下，股價由3元短期推上近15元，再單日急插九成。他慨嘆香港政治掛帥，「以往做超級中介人，食四方飯，唔需要take side，最重要係將兩邊問題收窄；如果你要take side，點都會得罪一邊。例如逼滙豐（005）表態，會有企業覺得唔舒服就走」。<br />\n<br />\n國際金融機構面對。。。。。。"},{"pid":"32ce163afc5cc6d02cba854b1c365f576ba32bf7","tid":2201931,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bee0bc2bc5e8d48a5f922d3266754a82a8be52e","tid":2201931,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"呢單應該推"}]}